@startuml
title Use cases – Package Caisse imprévue / Membership
left to right direction
skinparam actorStyle awesome

actor "Services Crédit spéciale" as Services
actor "Service CI/Membership" as CI

usecase "Vérifier statut à jour\n(client ou garant)" as UC_CheckStatus
usecase "Récupérer info membre/garant\n(nom, rôles, contacts)" as UC_GetMember
usecase "Consigner justification\nsi dérogation (non à jour)" as UC_Override
usecase "Remonter historique de fiabilité\n(pour score)" as UC_ScoreHistory

Services --> UC_CheckStatus
Services --> UC_GetMember
Services --> UC_Override
Services --> UC_ScoreHistory

UC_CheckStatus --> CI
UC_GetMember --> CI
UC_Override --> CI
UC_ScoreHistory --> CI

note right of UC_Override
  Cas particulier accepté par l'admin :
  emprunt autorisé malgré non-conformité.
end note

@enduml

